### API Endpoint Test Suite
### GET /api/tasting-notes

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/tasting-notes

### Test 1: Default parameters (no query params)
### Expected: 200 OK with mocked data, default pagination (page=1, limit=20)
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Test 2: Custom pagination (page=2, limit=10)
### Expected: 200 OK with pagination metadata showing page=2, limit=10
GET {{baseUrl}}?page=2&limit=10

### Test 3: Filter by brand_ids
### Expected: 200 OK (currently returns mocked data regardless of filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}?brand_ids=brand-001

### Test 4: Filter by min_rating
### Expected: 200 OK (currently returns mocked data regardless of filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}?min_rating=4

### Test 5: Sort by overall_rating DESC
### Expected: 200 OK (currently returns mocked data in fixed order)
GET {{baseUrl}}?sort_by=overall_rating&sort_order=desc

### Test 6: Invalid parameter - page = 0
### Expected: 400 Bad Request with validation error
GET {{baseUrl}}?page=0

### Test 7: Invalid parameter - limit > 100
### Expected: 400 Bad Request with validation error
GET {{baseUrl}}?limit=150

### Test 8: Invalid parameter - min_rating > 5
### Expected: 400 Bad Request with validation error
GET {{baseUrl}}?min_rating=6

### Test 9: Invalid parameter - invalid sort_by
### Expected: 400 Bad Request with validation error
GET {{baseUrl}}?sort_by=invalid_field

### Test 10: Invalid parameter - invalid UUID in brand_ids
### Expected: 400 Bad Request with validation error
GET {{baseUrl}}?brand_ids=not-a-uuid

### Test 11: Multiple filters combined
### Expected: 200 OK with mocked data
GET {{baseUrl}}?brand_ids=brand-001,brand-002&min_rating=3&sort_by=created_at&sort_order=asc&page=1&limit=20
